text: Novomikhaylovka () is a rural locality (a village) in Krivle-Ilyushkinsky Selsoviet, Kuyurgazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 2 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 36 km from Yermolayevo, 13 km from Krivle-Ilyushkino. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kuyurgazinsky District
title: Novomikhaylovka, Kuyurgazinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
